revision.text: =Mutating Berries= ''Note: if you have not yet unlocked all the plots on the farm and need to mutate berries #9 [[Persim]] through #25 [[Grepa]], please use the [https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TE5cAKSlA7TAliA001_mIiO1odZ6e4yUEMre0GBW1to/edit?usp=sharing Walkthrough link] for an optimized planting formation to mutate those berries within the limited available farm plots.''
